## 4. Business Source License 1.1

### (Governance & Tokenomics)

The following components are licensed under the **Business Source License (BSL) 1.1**:

* Governance mechanisms
* Voting logic
* Vesting, allocation, and token distribution logic

### License Parameters

* **Licensor:** VisionGaiaTechnology
* **Licensed Work:** GaiaComCoin Governance & Tokenomics Modules
* **Change Date:** 1 January 2029
* **Change License:** Apache License 2.0

### Use Limitation

The Licensed Work **may not be used** to operate, launch, or govern a competing public blockchain, cryptocurrency, or token network without explicit written permission from the Licensor.

After the Change Date, this code will automatically become available under the Apache License 2.0.

Full license text:
[https://mariadb.com/bsl11/](https://mariadb.com/bsl11/)

